headline: MDLZ Q3 Deep Dive: Volume Pressures and Pricing Actions Shape Near-Term Outlook
summary: Packaged snacks company Mondelez (NASDAQ:MDLZ) met Wall Streets revenue expectations in Q3 CY2025, with sales up 5.9% year on year to $9.74 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.73 per share was 2.9% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
